  <bodyText><![CDATA[
<p><em>Firstly: I'm aware that I am putting out another commerce
package into a crowded space. Please see below the video for my
thoughts on that.</em></p>

<p>The Video below is the first in a 3 (or maybe 4) part series on
creating a simple Umbraco cart using <a
href="http://our.umbraco.org/projects/website-utilities/doc-cart">Doc
Cart</a>, <a
href="http://our.umbraco.org/projects/umbraco-pro/courier">Courier</a>
and <a
href="http://our.umbraco.org/projects/backoffice-extensions/bill4u">
Bill4u</a>.</p>

<p><object width="520" height="390"
data="http://www.vimeo.com/moogaloop.swf?clip_id=23474861&amp;server=www.vimeo.com&amp;show_title=1&amp;show_byline=1&amp;show_portrait=0&amp;color=00ADEF&amp;fullscreen=1"
 type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="data"
